title: Colorful Facade
description: A colorful facade to a business or office. Great use of pastel colors and the contrast of the character's outfit.

title: Insane Building
description: Square building wrapped in an amazing mural, giving the depiction of having a 3D bricked surface.

title: Good Company
description: A blue, black, and white themed mural of people and humans enjoying animals, nature, and each other.

title: Alley Graffiti
description: 3-tiered graffiti on a black cinderblock surface in an alley.

title: Birthday Kitty
description: A cheetah/leopard wearing a birthday hat, painted on an electric/utility box. It doesn't look too happy.

title: Mickey Likes to Paint
description: Looks like Mickey Mouse, but angry and with a paint roller. What a guy!

title: Parking Lot Guardian
description: A huge robot overlooking the parking lot. The robot's gears can be seen, as well as vines surrounding it.

title: Ratigan Graffiti
description: The best Disney villain. I love 'The Great Mouse Detective'. This one is really cool!

title: Beachside Plant
description: A really pretty sculutpre of a potted plant, located in a beachside art park.

title: Ceramic Tower
description: A ceramic sculpture found in a fountain in downtown Greensboro.

title: Modern and Colorful Mural
description: A geometric and multi-colored mural that spans the side of a large building. Features a bust of a woman with blue and purple hair.

title: Geometric Archway
description: A silver archway made of square pipes of varying length. Fun photo spot!

title: They've Seen Some Stuff
description: A high-up mural that shows a person with paint/tears rolling down their face. Powerful for sure!

title: Classic Coca-Cola
description: A classic mural of Coca-Cola.

title: Rocky Statue
description: An interesting statue placed on a rock. Spotted in Charleston.

title: Wild One
description: A mural that has an egg-shaped creature screaming with a question mark coming out of its mouth. It also has blue fire behind it, which is always fun.

title: Star-Pyramid
description: A really cool pyramid, composed of iron and chipped away cement on the sides.

title: Here Comes the Train
description: 3D painted tunnel with the illusion of a train coming out. It's a great photo spot!

title: Colorful Distress
description: A colorful and dark mural of a female character who looks distressed.

title: Dystopian Palms
description: Freaky looking mural that looks like Squidward's house. Pink background with palm trees and frogs!

title: Diamond Lady
description: A lady with purple flowing hair and diamonds surrounding her. Quite lovely.

title: General Store
description: A small-town mural of a general store, on the side of the actual P.H. Morris General Store.

title: Addiction Awareness
description: A powerful mural advocating for addiction awareness.

title: Woman on the Bricks
description: A beautiful mural of a woman draped in fabric, painted on a brick surface.

title: A Scrolling Sea
description: Large mural of a ship in rough waters, on a rolled up scroll. Pretty neat!

title: The Witch
description: A spooky witch, maybe the one from Snow White, creating a poison apple.

title: Clifford and the Gang
description: Clifford the Big Red Dog hangs out with other cartoon characters on a bookshelf! Very nostalgic!

title: Alien Landscape
description: This amazing mural shows a desert landscape with two vehicles flying through the air.
